item.title: By: sammie o
item.dc:creator: sammie o
item.description: Well you know me I cant leave the house without my lipstick . Most of my best ones are drugstore brands . The only time I need to buy a 15 dollar lipstick is when I need a good matte that will stay on all day so thank you for sharing this because now I have a some good leads on how I can get those on the cheap.
